msg: Conversion from java.util.Calendar to com.ibm.icu.util.Calendar. I didn't convert the Cloud component - I wasn't sure if the Calendar class was being passed through SOAP.

I'll let the dust settle from this, then I'll add the user-selected calendar capability.
